        "action": "Reimburse contract termination fees",
        "additional_details": "As the UK goes into lockdown due to Covid-19 people will have to take time off work to look after kids due to school closures. This will cause financial hardship for thousands of families.",
        "background": "The Government should reimburse early termination fees for people who need to stop certain subscription services due to financial hardship as a result of Covid-19. For example, phone and broadband contracts. ",
